Subject: [PATCH 3/4] feat(exec): add main session policy for exec guard and
 SSH block

PERSONAL BUILD: Add ExecMainSessionPolicy type and enforcement:
- forbidLongExec: Block long-running foreground commands in main session
- blockSshCommands: Block SSH/SCP/SFTP commands in main session
- maxExecTimeoutSec: Maximum timeout for foreground exec (default 120s)
- requireBackgroundForExec: Force background mode for all exec

Main session detection via session key pattern matching.
SSH commands are detected via regex patterns for ssh, scp, sftp, rsync.
